alex.mojaki.boxes

Class ForwardingPowerBox<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • alex.mojaki.boxes.ForwardingPowerBox<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Box<T>, PowerBox<T>

    public abstract class ForwardingPowerBox<T>
extends Object
implements PowerBox<T>
    A PowerBox that wraps around another PowerBox and forwards the interface methods and toString. This is not useful on its own but makes it easy it to implement the decorator pattern by subclassing.
